                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <i class="fas fa-file-code"></i>
                        <span>EJS</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <i class="fab fa-markdown"></i>
                        <span>Markdown</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <i class="fab fa-css3-alt"></i>
                        <span>CSS3</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <i class="fab fa-js-square"></i>
                        <span>JavaScript</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Timeline Section -->
    <section class="about-section timeline-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">发展历程</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2024年</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h4>博客正式上线</h4>
                    <p>完成博客系统开发，开始定期发布技术文章和个人思考。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2023年</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h4>开始内容创作</h4>
                    <p>开始在各大技术平台分享文章，积累了一定的读者群体。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2022年</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h4>技术学习深入</h4>
                    <p>深入学习前端框架和后端技术，开始参与开源项目。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-date">2021年</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h4>编程之路开始</h4>
                    <p>开始学习编程，接触 Web 开发，对技术产生浓厚兴趣。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="about-section contact-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">联系我</h2>
        <div class="contact-content">
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p class="contact-intro">
                    如果你对博客内容有任何疑问，或者想要交流技术话题，欢迎通过以下方式联系我。
                    我很乐意与志同道合的朋友交流学习！
                </p>
                
                <div class="contact-methods">
                    <% if (config.social.email) { %>
                    <div class="contact-method">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <h4>邮箱</h4>
                            <p><a href="mailto:<%= config.social.email %>"><%= config.social.email %></a></p>
                            <span class="contact-note">工作日通常会在24小时内回复</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
                    
                    <% if (config.social.github) { %>
                    <div class="contact-method">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <h4>GitHub</h4>
                            <p><a href="<%= config.social.github %>" target="_blank">查看我的项目</a></p>
                            <span class="contact-note">欢迎 Star 和 Fork</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
                    
                    <div class="contact-method">
                        <div class="contact-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-rss"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="contact-details">
                            <h4>RSS 订阅</h4>
                            <p><a href="/rss.xml" target="_blank">订阅博客更新</a></p>
                            <span class="contact-note">第一时间获取最新文章</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Contact Form -->
            <div class="contact-form-container">
                <h3>发送消息</h3>
                <form class="contact-form" id="contactForm">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">姓名 *</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
